self.setUpClass()
nqubits = 2
k = ql.Kernel('kernel1', platf, nqubits)
k.prepz(0)
k.prepz(1)
k.x(0)
k.gate('cnot', [0, 1])
k.gate('rx90', [1])
k.clifford(1, 0)
k.measure(0)
sweep_points = [2]
p = ql.Program('rb_program', platf, nqubits)
p.set_sweep_points(sweep_points)
p.add_kernel(k)
p.compile()
